import { Component } from '@angular/core';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-tabs',
  templateUrl: 'tabs.page.html',
  styleUrls: ['tabs.page.scss']
})
export class TabsPage {

  constructor() {}

}
<ion-tabs>

  <ion-tab-bar slot="bottom">
    <ion-tab-button tab="tab1">
      <ion-icon aria-hidden="true" name="caret-back-outline"></ion-icon>
      <ion-label>Recents</ion-label>
    </ion-tab-button>

    <ion-tab-button tab="tab2">
      <ion-icon aria-hidden="true" name="caret-up-outline"></ion-icon>
      <ion-label>Favorites</ion-label>
    </ion-tab-button>

    <ion-tab-button tab="tab3">
      <ion-icon aria-hidden="true" name="caret-forward-outline"></ion-icon>
      <ion-label>Account</ion-label>
    </ion-tab-button>
  </ion-tab-bar>

</ion-tabs>
